data.description: STUNNING! Better than new and looks like a model! 4 bedrooms, plus an office 2 Bath, and 2 car garage CBS home situated on a private preserve lot. This home boasts a large great room with a sizable formal dining room. Adorned with designer finishes and upgrades including, luxury vinyl floors, shiplap, custom window treatments, ceiling fans, and light fixtures. Chef's dream kitchen with white cabinets, quartz countertops, beautiful backsplash, breakfast bar, and large center island. Luxurious owner's suite complete with a huge walk-in closet and a master bath that will make you feel like you are at the spa! Enjoy outdoor entertaining under the covered patio overlooking a tranquil preserve. Low HOA fee includes lawn and landscape, community resort-style pool, fitness center, tennis, and playground. Ideal location close to schools, shopping, dining, I-95, and FL TPK.
